lead_paragraph: The Cincinnati Reds had squandered 4-1 lead late in Saturday night's game and it seemed just a matter of time before the Washington Nationals completed a comeback win.

headline.print_headline: Reds Score 5 Runs in the 10th to Beat Nationals 9-4
